title: Swedish Charters Added by Germania for June - August 2016
text:
Swedish Charters Added by Germania for June - August 2016   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Between June and August 2016 Germania is operating a number of charter services from Sweden, which links Dusseldorf with Jonkoping and Umea, on board Boeing 737-700 aircraft. Planned schedules are as follows. 
Dusseldorf – Umea 02JUN16 / 09JUN16 / 16JUN16 / 21JUL16 / 28JUL16 / 04AUG16 ST5010 DUS1115 – 1345UME 73G
